==Torres Strait Creole==
===Noun===
'''[[musu]] [[koknat]]'''

# (''western dialect'') a [[sprout]]ing [[coconut]]
===Usage note===
''Musu koknat'' (western dialect) or ''[[giru]]'' (eastern dialect) is the second stage of coconut growth. It is preceded by ''[[musu]]'' (western dialect) or ''[[wai]]'' (eastern dialect), and followed by ''[[smol koknat]]'' (western dialect) or ''[[gad]]'' (eastern dialect).
===Synonyms===
*[[giru]] (''eastern dialect'')
